videos.headline: Idaho's Duckworth breaks free for 74 yards
videos.description: Aaron Duckworth escapes the defense as he scampers for a 74-yard run.

videos.headline: Idaho's Linehan finds Ungerer for TD
videos.description: Matt Linehan connects with David Ungerer to extend Idaho's lead.

videos.headline: WMU's Wassink hits Eskridge for TD
videos.description: Jon Wassink throws a touchdown pass to D'Wayne Eskridge to close the gap in the third quarter.

videos.headline: WMU's Bellamy sprints 19- yards for the TD
videos.description: LeVante Bellamy takes it in from 19-yards out to give the Broncos' their first lead of the game.

videos.headline: Linehan stretches out for TD
videos.description: Matt Linehan fully extends to take the lead back for the Vandals.

videos.headline: Linehan throws 2nd TD of the night
videos.description: Matt Linehan finds Alfonso Onuwor to extend Idaho's lead in the third quarter.

videos.headline: WMU's Jackson makes circus catch for interception
videos.description: Obbie Jackson catches the ball 3 times before finally coming down with the interception.

videos.headline: Wassink scores 2nd rushing TD of the night
videos.description: Jon Wassink punches it in from 1-yard out to retake the lead in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Bronco defense forces late game fumble
videos.description: Idaho's Matt Linehan gets the ball knocked loose after leaving the pocket and Western Michigan recovers.
